{"tid":96294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TRUMP：墨總統不為築牆付錢  就別訪美","createTime":"2017-01-26T17:12:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T08:58:19.000Z","uid":62257,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f3da5da92c2e0d31aeb78b6d319a23dda41947e7","tid":96294,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:12:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201701260364-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201701260364-1.aspx&d=STMkvUT9Oev8oTGP0AguHAT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=3afa9c50\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201701260364-1.aspx</a><br />\n（中央社華盛頓26日綜合外電報導）美國總統川普今天對墨西哥總統潘尼亞尼托（Enrique Pena Nieto）發出嚴厲的最後通牒，宣稱潘尼亞尼托若不願支付在兩國邊界築牆的經費，就「最好取消」訪美之行。<br />\n<br />\n川普推文表示：「美國對墨西哥有600億美元貿易逆差，從北美自由貿易協定（NAFTA）一實施，就呈現一面倒的狀況，使我方大量的就業機會和公司消失無蹤。」<br />\n<br />\n「如果墨西哥不願為急需的隔牆支付工程費用，那麼最好還是取消雙方即將舉行的會談。」1060126"},{"pid":"20aa1bf3436a81d71d21b809648a8f8fd1fa319d","tid":96294,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T17:14:15.000Z","msg":"Donald J. Trump已認證帳戶<br />\n&rlm;@realDonaldTrump<br />\n<br />\n 關注<br />\n 更多<br />\nof jobs and companies lost. If Mexico is unwilling to pay for the badly needed wall, then it would be better to cancel the upcoming meeting."},{"pid":"2f08899a5d3d513f0857ca695ca6ff4e41004497","tid":96294,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T18:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6a1d53a82f42085989a5d1616a1e472d6931e4","tid":96294,"uid":36857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T18:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792d4fbaeacaa22e0bbd546651191bc92ffa297d","tid":96294,"uid":7